data.title: Letter to Secretary Hillary Rodham Clinton, Department of State
data.meta_description: On March 17, 2011 Congressman Burgess and 301 Members of Congress sent a letter to Secretary Hillary Rodham Clinton, Department of State, regarding the events in Egypt. To view the letter as a PDF click on the image below.
